# Collision detection / response test arena
# Scale is metric. Player is ~1.8m tall (eye at y=1.8).
#
# Layout (looking north from spawn, +z = north, +x = east):
#
#                                NORTH
#     +--------------------------------------------------------+
#     |              upper platform (y=3m)                     |
#     |     west:                       east:                  |
#     |     multi-level                 stacked jump-stairs    |
#     |     platforms                   stepping stones        |
#     |     + ramps                     + tall stack           |
#     |                                                        |
#     |        << main 15-step staircase (rise 3m) >>          |
#     |                                                        |
#     |     pillars / corners / narrow gaps / low ceiling      |
#     |        small-step row     (path tests)     pit         |
#     |                                                        |
#     |                    SPAWN PLAZA                         |
#     +--------------------------------------------------------+
#                                SOUTH

